      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just that the \"people who care\" part feels so theoretical. like, i check my notifications and it's just apps and spam. even at work, i'm just a profile picture on a screen. no one actually sees me. if i just stopped... wouldn't it just be a relief for everyone if they didn't have to deal with the hollow version of me anymore? it feels like i'm just taking up space that isn't even mine.",
